Generic single-database configuration.

In this project, it will have a database for a particular showroom for cars. It will be named:

showroom.db

Our showroom.db will have three tables:

    showrooms - will display name of showrrom and its location

    carowners - will display first name and last name of the car owner

    cars - will display car details of the car

The relationships will be:

    Showroom has one-to-many relationship with cars table
    Showroom has one-to-many relationship with carowners table
    Carowner has one-to-many relationship with cars table
    Car has many-to-one relationship with showroom
    Car has many-to-one relationship with car owner